LOOPS-


WHILE LOOP-

#!/usr/bin/ruby

$i=0
$num=5

while $i < $num do
  puts " inside the loop i = #$i "
  $i +=1
end


OUTPUT-
 inside the loop i = 0 
 inside the loop i = 1 
 inside the loop i = 2 
 inside the loop i = 3 
 inside the loop i = 4


WHILE MODIFIER-

#!bin/usr/ruby

$i=0
$num=5

begin
  puts"inside the loop i = #$i"
  $i+=1

end  while $i < $num

OUTPUT-
inside the loop i = 0
inside the loop i = 1
inside the loop i = 2
inside the loop i = 3
inside the loop i = 4
 
